---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
import "../styles/base.css";
---

<Layout title="Mentorship">
  <PageHeader
    overline="Tech for Palestine"
    title="Mentorship"
    subtitle="Connect with experienced professionals and grow your skills while advancing Palestinian freedom"
  />

  <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8 pb-24">
    
    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
        <p class="text-xl leading-8 text-gray-600 mb-8">
          Our mentorship program connects passionate individuals with experienced professionals 
          in the tech industry who are committed to Palestinian liberation. Whether you're looking 
          to develop your technical skills, advance your career, or amplify your impact, 
          our community is here to support your journey.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      
      <!-- For Mentees -->
      <section class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">For Mentees</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">What You'll Gain</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Career guidance from industry veterans
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Technical skill development and code reviews
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Networking within the pro-Palestine tech community
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Opportunities to contribute to meaningful projects
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-green-800 mb-3">Who Should Apply</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Early-career developers and designers</li>
              <li>• Students pursuing tech-related fields</li>
              <li>• Career changers entering tech</li>
              <li>• Anyone passionate about using tech for Palestinian liberation</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4">
            <a
              href="/volunteer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-green-700 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-green-800 transition-colors"
            >
              Apply to be a Mentee
              <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- For Mentors -->
      <section class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-6">For Mentors</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-800 mb-3">Your Impact</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Shape the next generation of pro-Palestine technologists
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Share your expertise to advance our collective mission
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Build meaningful connections within our community
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-600 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
                Contribute to projects that create real change
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-red-800 mb-3">Mentor Requirements</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• 3+ years of professional tech experience</li>
              <li>• Commitment to Palestinian liberation</li>
              <li>• Available for 2-4 hours per month</li>
              <li>• Strong communication skills</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="pt-4">
            <a
              href="/volunteer"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-red-700 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-red-800 transition-colors"
            >
              Apply to be a Mentor
              <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- How It Works Section -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-4">How It Works</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">A simple process to connect mentors and mentees</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800">1</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Apply</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Fill out our application form with your background, goals, and availability.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800">2</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Match</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We carefully pair mentors and mentees based on experience, goals, and interests.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="bg-blue-100 rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-800">3</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Connect</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Begin your mentorship journey with regular meetings and ongoing support.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Call to Action Section -->
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-600 to-red-600 rounded-lg p-8 text-center text-white">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-green-800">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-green-800">Join our mentorship program and help build a more ethical tech industry that supports Palestinian liberation.</p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="/volunteer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white text-green-700 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
        >
          Apply Now
        </a>
        <a
          href="/discord-invite"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-white text-green-700 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
        >
          Join Our Discord
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mt-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How much time commitment is required?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We recommend 2-4 hours per month for meaningful mentorship relationships. This can be flexible based on both parties' availability and needs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What areas of expertise are most needed?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We welcome mentors from all areas of tech including software development, design, product management, data science, DevOps, and more. Non-technical skills like project management and marketing are also valuable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I participate if I'm not Palestinian?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Absolutely! Our community welcomes allies who are committed to Palestinian liberation and want to use their skills and privilege to support the cause.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibent text-gray-900 mb-2">How are mentors and mentees matched?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">We consider factors like technical expertise, career goals, time zones, and personal interests to create meaningful partnerships that benefit both parties.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>